    <header>
        
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h3>About Us</h3>
            <p>Welcome to our e-commerce store! We are dedicated to providing the best electronic gadgets to our customers. Our mission is to deliver quality products and exceptional customer service.</p>
            <p>From smartphones to smartwatches, we have everything you need to stay connected and productive.</p>
            <h4>Our Values</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Quality</li>
                <li>Innovation</li>
                <li>Customer Satisfaction</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Electromart. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
